query:
WITH duplicados AS (
  SELECT cnpj
  FROM clientes
  WHERE cnpj IS NOT NULL AND cnpj != ''
  GROUP BY cnpj
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
  LIMIT 10
)
SELECT 
  c.id,
  c.cnpj,
  c.nome,
  c.createdAt,
  c.qualidadeScore,
  c.email,
  c.telefone,
  c.siteOficial,
  c.produtoPrincipal,
  c.cidade,
  c.uf,
  CASE 
    WHEN c.email IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
    CASE WHEN c.telefone IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
    CASE WHEN c.siteOficial IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
    CASE WHEN c.produtoPrincipal IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
    CASE WHEN c.cidade IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
    CASE WHEN c.uf IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as campos_preenchidos
FROM clientes c
INNER JOIN duplicados d ON c.cnpj = d.cnpj
ORDER BY c.cnpj, c.id;
